messages.message: Hey all, been seeing a slow trickle of bugs come in with this recent June 21.6.0 release to prod. Can we try to track these bugs in the UAT sheet to get a better sense of our testing gaps this release? https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1x0RIBNi4Q71FF1L5tqBsRa08hpcRhxuUn9dwuDNxRys/edit#gid=803482741
I put everything we worked on in the spreadsheet
@Erick lydia mentioned you might have had a bug-fest this morning as well?

@Kerry I just updated it to make it clear flow is a secondary suspect — it sounded like Nidhi found a bug that could be causing it, and I just added the flow comment because Seb was specifically running into issues when “Delete Previous Output” was enabled, which he wasn’t before the release
Got it, let me follow up on that thread, see if there’s anything flow needs to fix
